<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Zion, kinin na nasep semzo di'n,
 Pathien vak ahih gam tin a gen di'n;
 Amah chitin leh nam tincheng Siempa chun,
 Kuomah zan thim a a man A deih puo'i.

[V2]
 Chanchin Pha phuong un,
 Muonna thu chuh;
 Isu tatna leh suohchakna Thu Pha chuh.

[V3]
 2. En u'n, mi sang tamtak thimnuoi ah a um ui,
 Gitlohna suongkul a sal a tang in;
 Hukdampa thih kuoma'n amau a hilh puoi,
 Amau hinna dinga thi ahih thu.

[V4]
 3. Mitin, pautin, namtin kawmah phuongzak in,
 A hinnau Pathien Lungsietna a hih;
 A siemsa mangthaite chuh hukdamna di'n,
 A hung thii mi'n van hinna a neih na'n.

[V5]
 4. Thu vaithak lopi gen ding na chate pie'n,
 Na neih cheng le Chanchin Pha genna'n pie'n;
 Amau di'n na lunggil pumpi'n paucham in,
 Na sen cheng Isu'n hun din vek ina.

[V6]
 5. Aw Zion, Amah hungkit chuh na tuok ma'n,
 Mi cheng A hehpih, hukdam thu hilh in;
 Na ngaihsak loh zieka mi mangthai lo a,
 A mel mu taklo a um lohna di'n.</lyrics>
<title>O ZION, HASTE</title>
<hymn_number>199</hymn_number>
</song>